queryLines:
SELECT business_usecase_type, COUNT(*) AS usecase_count, SUM(estimated_monthly_dollar_dbus)
FROM users.luis_herrera.pipelineiq_view
GROUP BY business_usecase_type
ORDER BY usecase_count DESC
LIMIT 10;

lines:
# Confidence Pulse
High Bankable Pipeline
Use cases with high confidence are well-qualified, low-risk, and fully aligned with MEDDPICC. The champion, metrics, and decision path are clear execution can proceed with confidence. These are your high-conviction commits: accelerate, remove friction, and replicate what works.

Medium Coachable Pipeline
Use cases with medium confidence show strong potential but contain qualification gaps perhaps the champion is weak, the value unproven, or the decision process unclear. Progress is possible, but only through targeted intervention. Leaders should coach, requalify, or rescope before more investment to bring these deals back on track.

Low Forecast Noise
Use cases with low confidence carry significant uncertainty or flawed assumptions. Missing metrics, absent champions, or unknown path to production signal that fundamentals need rebuilding. These arent lost use cases yet they need rework to regain clarity before investing more Pause, requalify, or redirect effort to protect forecast integrity and team focus.

The table below provides a one-liner summary of each use case, along with an AI-generated confidence score assessing its health from a MEDDPICC perspective. It also includes a recommendation (walk/re-inspect, adapt/pivot, or proceed) and the top three drivers influencing the confidence level. You can obtain a more detailed tactical advice on any use case using [this Glean Agent](https://databricks.glean.com/chat/agents/e86cb3d6138a47d18a664e57d4af3c6d) go/uc-doctor-agent

**Use cases going live the next 6 months that are likely to slip** You can check out any of the Glean agents below to dive in and get tailored advice based on your specific use case: go/uc-doctor-agent Diagnose UC health directly from Salesforce link to use case.
go/stakeholder-outreach-agent Build executive outreach plans tied to business priorities.
go/onboarding-review-agent Review onboarding plans to surface gaps, friction, and blockers.
go/value-soundbite-agent Turn technical work into crisp business-impact messages.
go/poc-review-agent Optimize PoC plans to deliver outcomes faster.
